title: Oce end of season rewards
body: When is OCE going to get 2015 end of season rewards, i would have thought we would get them first since our season ended a day before, will we get them soon, or on the 17th?

replies.body: Season Rewards will come out throughout the days up until the 17th of November.
But will OCE get it in a certain date or time?

Rewards were given out yesterday and will be given out everyday up until the 17th of November for OCE.
For more information about these Ranked Rewards, click [here](http://oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/page/2015-ranked-season-draws-close).
Rewards are given out in waves until the 17th so you might get them with any wave.
The season rewards will be given out until the 17th.On the 17th is where all rewards have been given out.
